<div class="container my-5 container-home">
  <div class="home-top-section">
    <div class="home-top-section-text d-flex flex-column align-items-start justify-content-center">
      <h1>Welcome to MinaNoka!</h1>
      <h3>Rent the perfect field!</h3>
      <p>MinaNoka rental lifestyle in the countryside. The field farmer rental lifestyle is a great way to live out your dreams of living in nature. You'll have access to a wide variety of crops, fruits and vegetables that you can grow yourself and sell or use as part of your own business.</p>
      <%= link_to 'Find a field', fields_path, class:"btn btn-lg btn-primary px-3 mt-3 w-fit" %>
    </div>
    <div class="home-img"
         style="background-image:url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1622383563227-04401ab4e5ea?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=774&q=80);">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="my-5">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2">
      <h2>Most popular fields</h2>
      <p class="mb-0"><%= link_to "see more", fields_path %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="row cards-home g-2">
      <% @fields.each do |field|  %>
        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
          <%= render "fields/card", field: field  %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="my-5">
    <h2>What is MinaNoka?</h2>
    <p>
      Japan is known for its rich farming tradition, and we believe that you should be able to experience that tradition too! That’s why we’ve made it easy for you to get in on the action with our Japan Farming Experience.
      Our Japan Farming Experience lets you rent a field and grow your own crops, just like they do in Japan.
    </p>
    <p>
      You’ll get your own plot of land, and all the seeds, tools, and knowledge you need to grow some amazing plants—you can even plant rice!
      We know how stressful life can be sometimes, so we want you to be able to take some time out of your day and relax as you tend to your crops. We offer this service at three different locations across Japan: Kyoto, Tokyo, and Osaka.
    </p>
    <p>
      So if you’re looking for an escape from the hustle and bustle of city life or just want a unique way to spend time with your family or friends, then this might just be the thing for you!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
